ActControlled Drugs and Substances Act
Food and Drugs Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS by adding ten substances to the lists of controlled substances set out in various schedules to the Regulations, and by deleting the references to Etryptamine and its salts, to Glutethimide and to Pemoline and its salts, all of which are presently listed in Part I of Schedule F.
